\begin_layout Standard
This projects aims at grouping utilities to deal with the numerous and heterogen
ous information retrieval (IR) test collections, and to automate/standardize
 common operations like downloading topics, assessments or evaluating.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Each IR task has a unique identifier.
 For example, the ad-hoc track of TREC-1 has the identifier trec.1/adhoc.
\end_layout

